      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) عَنْ رَجُلٍ قَالَ لآِخَرَ يَا فَاسِقُ قَالَ لَا حَدَّ عَلَيْهِ وَ يُعَزَّرُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Al Qasim Bin Muhammad Al Miqary, from Al Noman Bin Abdul Salam, from Abu Haneefa who said, ",
          "‘I asked Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> about a man who said to another, ‘O wicked!’ He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘There is no Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>) upon him, and he would be reprimanded’."
        ]
      }
